nput stellar models play an important role in\ndetermining which regions of the binary parameter space can produce compact\nbinary mergers, paving the way for current and future gravitational-wave\nprogenitor predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-21"}
